Depends :
---------
XiVO:
- xivo-dao
- lib-python

Other dependencies will be installed by the install script:
- Flask-0.6-1, Werkzeug-0.6.2-1, 

Installation :
--------------
use xivo-recording.tar

tar -xvf xivo-recording.tar
cd xivo-recording

Be sure to have a corresponding web interface package in the xivo-recording directory (with the support of the recording)! 
./install.sh


Packaging :
-----------
Create the tar
tar -cvf xivo-restapi.tar xivo-restapi/ --exclude '*.log' --exclude '.*' --exclude '*.pyc' --exclude tests --exclude acceptance


Test:
-----

curl --digest --user admin:passadmin http://192.168.51.14:50050/1.0/recording_campaigns/ --insecure -c cookie.txt -b cookie.txt --header "Accept: application/json" 
